  "plan": "1. Navigate to the target directory /home/user. 2. Create the directory if it doesn't exist. 3. Examine the diagnostics.ini configuration file to extract required parameters (NET_IFACE, PING_HOST). 4. Begin data collection for the JSON output file. 5. Generate the network_data.json file with proper structure and encoding. 6. Create the human-readable report file with consistent data. 7. Set proper permissions on both files. 8. Verify the integrity hash matches between the files.",
